quran[27]{c,v,t}:
  37,127,"Mana nibamuyingasia. Ne toto balikhung’asibwa (mumulilo)."
  37,128,"Halali Abasumba ba Nyasaye Abatswenulwa."
  37,129,"Mana nikhumuleshela ifuma indayi khubalia betsa inyuma wuwe."
  37,130,"Omulembe kube khu Ilyas."
  37,131,"Toto endio nilwa khurunganga Abalayi."
  37,132,"Toto ye ali Mubasumba befu Abasuubila."
  37,133,"Ne toto Luti ali Mubarumwa."
  37,134,"Olwa khwamuhabina halala nende Abandu baye boosi."
  37,135,"Halali omukhasi omushiele owali mubatong’a inyuma (mubasishibwa)."
  37,136,"Mana nikhusishia abandi abo."
  37,137,"Ne toto enywe mubaburangakhwo mumabwibwi."
  37,138,"Nende eshilo, mana kho shimukharetsangakhwo mubwongo tawe?"
  37,139,"Ne toto Yunus yali mulala khubarumwa."
  37,140,"Olwa yelushila muliaro litsule."
  37,141,"Mana nibasanjilana mumakhuwa, mana nikamukwiila obubi."
  37,142,"Mana inyeni nimumila naye nali ufunaanibwa."
  37,143,"Ne akhayanga okhuba mubalia abatswenulanga Nyasaye."
  37,144,"Yakhamenyele munda mwayo okhuula inyanga yokhulamusibwa mubafu."
  37,145,"Mana nikhumusukuna khulukuku, naye nali omulwale."
  37,146,"Ne nikhumumesilia omumela kwelihondo."
  37,147,"Mana nikhumuruma khubandu iyelefu imia ndala nohomba bashilaho awo."
  37,148,"Mana nibasuubila, ne nikhubara mubwokholo okhula okhufwa khwabu."
  37,149,"Ne bareebe mbu: “Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi niye uli nende abana abakhana nabo bali nende abana abasiani?"
  37,150,"Nohomba khwaloonga Abamalaika okhuba beshikhasi nabo nibalolanga?”"
  37,151,"Ne toto manya mbu khububeyi bwabu baboolanga mbu:"
  37,152,"“Nyasaye yebula”, ne toto bo nababeyi."
  37,153,"Oh, yalobola abana beshikhana okhushila beshisiani?"